title: Jeppesen FliteStar/Flitemap RASTER CHARTS EUROPE 2007
description:
A nice addition for FS/FM users especially Europeans.

Just copy the contents from CD into your FliteStar folder CHARTS\RASTER and then via Flitestars menu, Chart | Load Chart | RasterPlus , and the program will recognize the charts and then display onscreen with a Hide/ShowRaster option. If right-clicked near the border line the respective chart open and appears on screen. These type of charts (TPC) are mainly used by MIL pilots and trainees.

Enjoy
